OL,3,CPub landlord returns to La Folie Inn
OL,4,C20 years since its closure
OL,6,FOne person who might have an idea or
OL,7,Ftwo as to what they would like to see
OL,8,Fdone with it is former pub landlord,
OL,9,FChris Melville, who became the
OL,10,Flicensee in 1988.
OL,12,FChris told ITV: "It was a bit crazy
OL,13,Fbut absolutely excellent, I mean
OL,14,Fpeople used to come in and plonk a
OL,15,Ftray of fish in the hallway and
OL,16,Fcustomers would help themselves.
OL,18,F"It was a one-off - there was no place
OL,19,Flike La Folie."
