OL,3,CPub landlord returns to La Folie Inn
OL,4,C20 years since its closure
OL,6,FChris has not stepped back inside the
OL,7,FLa Folie Inn since it closed its doors
OL,8,F20 years ago, until now.
OL,10,FITV Channel arranged to take Chris
OL,11,Fback into his old pub, for one last
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FOnce inside, Chris said: "This brings
OL,15,Fback memories (...) I can't serve you
OL,16,Fwith a pint but I can reminisce.
