OL,3,CPub landlord returns to La Folie Inn
OL,4,C20 years since its closure
OL,6,FHe added: "It's funny how time goes by
OL,7,F- it seems smaller than it was. It's
OL,8,Flike someone's thrown a hand grenade
OL,9,Fin here and waited for the dust to
OL,10,Fsettle."
OL,12,FThe pub's now dust-ridden rooms act as
OL,13,Fa time capsule to a bygone era, with
OL,14,Fold newspaper stands, pub trophies,
OL,15,Fand drinks menus left inside.
OL,17,FOne thing that has not changed in 20
OL,18,Fyears is the snacks that were offered
OL,19,Fto peckish punters.
