OL,3,CPub landlord returns to La Folie Inn
OL,4,C20 years since its closure
OL,6,FA note pinned to the wall details the
OL,7,Fprice of a bag of crisps (30p), a Mars
OL,8,Fbar (40p), and a packet of scampi
OL,9,Ffries (50p).
OL,11,FChris says: "I don't think I've ever
OL,12,Fseen the bar with an inch of dust on
OL,13,Fit and all the beer pumps with no beer
OL,14,Fat the end of them.
OL,16,F"It's sad, but times change and time
OL,17,Fgoes on and we all change with it."
