OL,3,CPub landlord returns to La Folie Inn
OL,4,C20 years since its closure
OL,6,FPorts of Jersey is running a market
OL,7,Fconsultation to assess the level of
OL,8,Finterest in developing the entire La
OL,9,FFolie site, including the former pub.
OL,11,FThey are open to ideas from interested
OL,12,Forganisations with proven experience
OL,13,Fin developing and managing high-
OL,14,Fquality visitor accommodation and
OL,15,Fhospitality venues.
OL,17,FChris has his own views on the pub's
OL,18,Ffuture, suggesting: "I'd like to see
OL,19,Fit as a small bar somewhere for the
OL,20,Fguys who are working on the boats.
